text: "The Take Over, The Breaks Over" (the quotes are a part of the name) is a 2007 song by the band Fall Out Boy. It was released in 2007 on their album Infinity on High. == Music video == The video focuses on Pete Wentz's dog, Hemmingway. The video, which was made in black and white, shows Hemmingway in a dream. Category:Fall Out Boy songs Category:2007 songs
title: The Take Over, the Breaks Over
